@startuml
' Diagram: F03b - Hang doi audio thuyet minh per-device (Activity, sub-activity cua F03)
' Status: VERIFIED
' Baseline: branch master, current worktree @ HEAD 2497a96
' Source:
' - VinhKhanhTourDemo/MainPage.xaml.cs: QueuePoiPlayback(), ProcessSpeakQueueAsync(), SpeakPoiAsync(), LogPlaybackAsync(), ShowNowPlaying(), HideNowPlaying()
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Controllers/ThuyetMinhController.cs: GetByPoi()
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Controllers/LogController.cs: Post()
' Note: So do tach rieng phan hang doi audio per-device de F03 khong qua tai. Day la queue *trong 1 thiet bi* (1 nguoi dung), KHONG phai server-side queue khi nhieu khach cung vao 1 quan.
' Note: Server khong xep hang theo POI. Khi nhieu khach o cung 1 POI, moi may tu quan ly queue cua minh; chong trung audio = cooldown 10 phut + dedup _queuedSpeakPoiIds + _playingPoi check.
' Note: 3 lop chong trung khi user di chuyen lien tuc giua nhieu POI:
'   1. _playingPoi.Id == poi.Id           -> POI dang phat: skip
'   2. _queuedSpeakPoiIds.Contains(poi.Id) -> da co trong queue: skip
'   3. _speakLock semaphore                -> serial hoa TTS, chi 1 SpeakAsync chay 1 luc
title F03b - Hang doi audio thuyet minh per-device

|MainPage / Caller|
start
:Caller goi QueuePoiPlayback(poi);
note right
  Caller gom: F03 geofence trigger,
  va nut "Nghe lai" (OnListenClicked)
  trong MainPage.
end note

|QueuePoiPlayback|
:lock(_speakQueueGate);
if (_playingPoi != null VA _playingPoi.Id == poi.Id?) then (Co - dang phat POI nay)
  :return (skip, khong enqueue);
  note right: Tranh ghi de chinh POI dang phat
  stop
elseif (_queuedSpeakPoiIds.Contains(poi.Id)?) then (Co - da co trong queue)
  :return (skip, khong enqueue);
  note right
    Vi du: user di lap di lap lai
    quanh mep POI A -> dwell trigger
    nhieu lan -> chi enqueue 1 lan.
  end note
  stop
else (chua co)
  :_speakQueue.Enqueue(poi);
  :_queuedSpeakPoiIds.Add(poi.Id);
  if (_isProcessingSpeakQueue?) then (Co)
    :unlock va tra ve\n(processor cu se dequeue tiep);
  else (Khong)
    :_isProcessingSpeakQueue = true;
    :shouldStartProcessor = true;
  endif
endif
:unlock(_speakQueueGate);

if (shouldStartProcessor?) then (Co)
  :MainThread.BeginInvokeOnMainThread(\n  () => _ = ProcessSpeakQueueAsync());
else (Khong)
  stop
endif

|ProcessSpeakQueueAsync|
while (true) is (loop drain queue)
  :lock(_speakQueueGate);
  if (_speakQueue.Count == 0?) then (Co - rong)
    :_isProcessingSpeakQueue = false;
    :unlock + return;
    stop
  else (Khong)
    :poi = _speakQueue.Dequeue();
    :_queuedSpeakPoiIds.Remove(poi.Id);
    :unlock(_speakQueueGate);
    :await SpeakPoiAsync(poi);
  endif
endwhile

|SpeakPoiAsync(poi)|
:await _speakLock.WaitAsync();
note right
  Semaphore serial hoa TTS:
  ngay ca khi processor bi goi
  song song (race), chi 1 SpeakAsync
  chay tai 1 thoi diem.
end note
:GET /api/thuyet-minh/{poiId}?lang=langCode;
if (Co NoiDung tu API?) then (Co)
  :content = NoiDung;
else (Khong)
  :content = "Chao mung ban den {TenPOI}"\n(fallback theo langCode);
endif
:_playingPoi = poi;
:ShowNowPlaying(poi);
:RenderPoiCards();
:await TextToSpeech.SpeakAsync(content, locale);
if (Throw exception?) then (Co)
  :Log error;
  :Speak fallback "Welcome to {TenPOI}";
endif
:LogPlaybackAsync(poi.Id, langCode);
:POST /api/log (Nguon=GPS);
:_playingPoi = null;
:HideNowPlaying();
:RenderPoiCards();
:_speakLock.Release();
stop
@enduml
